CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 17, 1970, pg. 6, reads: "Church Leaders Celebrate - The exclusive dining area at the Top of The Towers was the scene of the Pre Christmas Dinner Party given by the Baptist Ministers and their wives recently. Some of the sponsors and key participants are pictured above. Center photo, reading from left, Rev. and Mrs. G. L. Bowick, Rev. George Kendall, guest speaker; Rev. and Mrs. Isaac Green.  Mrs. Bowick is president of the Baptist Ministers Wives Assoc., and chairman of the occasion.  Rev. Green is moderator of the Pittsburgh Area AUBA and presided for the evening... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Rev. G. L. Bowick, Mrs. Bowick, Rev. George Kendall, Mrs. Isaac Green, and Rev. Isaac Green, at Baptist Ministers pre-Christmas dinner, Top of the Towers restaurant
